                        Explore each photographer’s profile, view their portfolio, pricing, and reviews.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="step-card" data-step>
                    <div class="step-icon">📅</div>
                    <div class="step-title">Step 3: Contact or Book</div>
